cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with computer vision techniques for tracking high-fidelity face models from a commodity camera. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves graphics techniques for creating the high-fidelity face models, which falls under cs.GR (Computer Graphics). Additionally, the paper involves machine learning techniques for training the network, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also involves self-supervised learning, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper involves adapting to new environments, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
